videos.headline: Temple strikes first on a 13-yard TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King's scores on a 13-yard touchdown run on the reverse in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Houston's Davis interception sets up the Cougars
videos.description: Garrett Davis interception and return for 28-yards denies the Owls.

videos.headline: Wright hurdles defender for a first down
videos.description: Temple's Isaiah Wright hurdles a defender en route to a 22-yard gain and a first down.

videos.headline: Temple's Randall slams Dunbar
videos.description: Delvon Randall stops Steven Dunbar with a WWE bodyslam on a tackle.

videos.headline: Temple's Bradley ejected for targeting penalty
videos.description: Shaun Bradley hits Houston's Linell Bonner with a forearm and is ejected from the game.

videos.headline: Bonner's 9-yard TD catch extends the lead
videos.description: Kyle Postma and Linell Bonner connect for a 9-yard touchdown in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Hood scores TD for Temple
videos.description: David Hood scores from 1-yard out for the first TD of the day for Temple.

videos.headline: Davis interception seals Houston's win
videos.description: Logan Marchi's hail mary is intercepted by Garrett Davis to seal Houston's 20-13 win.
